# Typography System

Full spec: `.ai/design-system/typography.md`

## Font roles (never mix)

| Role | Font | Elements |
|------|------|----------|
| Serif | Playfair | H1, H2, display, stat numbers |
| Sans | Inter | H3–H6, body, nav, buttons, labels, forms |
| Mono | JetBrains | code, tech stack, terminal |

## Rules

- Use `var(--font-serif|sans|mono)` - never hardcode font names
- Use `--text-*` tokens from `styles/tokens.css` for sizes
- H3+ must be **sans**; H1/H2 must be **serif**
- No inline `fontFamily` / `fontSize` in TSX - use CSS classes (e.g. `.form-box-title`, `.label`)
- Add new text styles to `styles/typography.css`, not component files

## CSS import order

`tokens.css` → `typography.css` → `aetheris.css` → `product.css` (via `globals.css`)
